mTrip,develops,mobile,solutions,for,the,travel,industry,The,mTrip,API,can,be,used,by,tour,operators,travel,agencies,and,their,partners,to,sync,client,side,data,systems,with,the,mTrip,platform,The,mTrip,API,could,be,used,to,add,traveler,s,trip,information,into,a,rd,party,application,including,data,on,transportation,options,activities,accommodations,and,more,tailoring,specific,travel,guide,information,to,Individual,travelers